PDB (Protein Data Bank)
## 📌 Purpose

PDB stores experimentally determined 3D protein structures.

## 📌 Common Uses
Download protein structures
Visualize ligands
Structural analysis
Protein modeling studies

## 📌 Important File Formats
PDB (.pdb)
CIF

## 📌 Information Available
Resolution
Chains
Ligands
Experimental method
Authors

## 📌 Files to Upload
PDB structures
Structure screenshots
Ligand images
Protein details report
